· Location: NRHO (Near Rectilinear Halo Orbit)
· Capacity: 2,000 tons LH2/LOX annually
· Utilization rate: Year 1-3: 30%, Year 4-6: 60%, Year 7+: 85%
· Price: $500/kg (vs. $2,000/kg from Earth)
· OpEx: $200M/year fixed + $50/kg variable

