· Annual OpEx: $400M
· Return flights (every 2 years): $300M/flight
· Total 20-year OpEx: $8B (PV)

Revenue Model

Production Schedule:

· Year 6-10: 10 tons PGMs/year + 10,000 tons base metals
· Year 11-20: 20 tons PGMs/year + 20,000 tons base metals
· Year 21-30: 30 tons PGMs/year + 30,000 tons base metals

Price Assumptions:

· PGMs: Start $30,000/kg, declining 5%/year due to increased supply
· Base metals: $2/kg constant
· Orbital delivery premium: 50% over terrestrial prices

